column1: Regular traffic reports will resume Thursday September 20 at 4:00 p.m.

column4: Roadway shutdown at Exit 15 in Whitley Co until further notice due to a semi collision with large fuel spill near the TN line.
Detour:  US-25 at Exit 15 to Jellico, and back to I-75S.
UPDATE 3:00 p.m.:  Roadway is open.  Expect continued delays while traffic returns to normal.
